statement:
select   person.id
FROM   (select * from person where person.tenant_id = 1681) person   
LEFT JOIN 
    (select * from virtual_external_user where tenant_id = 1681) virtual_external_user
    ON  CAST(     get_json_string (person._acc_fields, '$.sDR_Owner__c') AS VARCHAR   ) = virtual_external_user.external_id 
WHERE
    get_json_string(virtual_external_user.fields, '$.name') IS NOT NULL
